<h1><span id="Ruy_Lopez:_Exchange_Variation">Ruy Lopez: Exchange Variation</span></h1>
<p>White decides they don't want to risk having their Bishop trapped on the queenside, and exchanges it with black's Knight. Black's only good move is 4...dxc6, as 4...bxc6 leaves white with a small advantage.
</p>
